<main>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="jumbotron">
        <h2 class="display-2 text-center pt-3 p-3 text-light">
          Welcome to ScannPal!
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row ">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="jumbotron bg-teal p-4 rounded-4">
          <h4 class="display-5 pb-4">What is ScannPal?</h4>
          <p>Developed by Justin, Matteo, and Adam, ScannPal utilizes Amazon Web Services (AWS) to sprinkle a massive workload throughout multiple cloud instances to speed up tasks. Please do not scan websites without permission.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">    
            
        </div>
        
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">    
            
        </div>
