          <div class="jumbotron bg-blueish p-4 rounded-4">
            <h4 class="display-5 mb-4">Functionality</h4>
            <p>You can start a scan in the Scan Page with a valid username, password, and URL. To see the results of previous scans, visit the Results page.</p>
          </div>
        </div>


    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="jumbotron bg-grayish p-4 rounded-4">
          <h4 class="display-5 mb-4">Mission</h4>
          <p>Our mission is to give website owners the ability to seamlessly secure their websites. We hope that our application can make the internet a safer place for all.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">    
            
        </div>
        
    </div>
